                 <div class=\"article-content\">\n                        <h3>Culinary Adventures: Spice It Up!</h3>\n                        <p>Embark on a flavorful journey with recipes that are bold, vibrant, and exciting. Learn to master the art of spice.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n                    </div>\n                </article>\n                <article class=\"article-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/c01a1a/ffffff?text=Article+4\" alt=\"Article 4 Image\">\n                    <div class=\"article-content\">\n                        <h3>The Rise of Digital Art</h3>\n                        <p>A look into the evolving landscape of digital art, its impact on the creative industry, and its accessibility to new artists.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\">Read More &rarr;</a>\n                    </div>\n                </article>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Vibrant Reads Magazine. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}